AccessComments:
Key required from Visitor Centre desk.  Cables (Type 1 and Type 2) available to borrow (or you can use your own) but the key is required to access the cabinet in any case.

The space in front of the charger is not reserved for EVs, but is marked "15 minute parking only, unless charging"
